  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the Jewish mothers were using it for knitting [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] caps and scarves for those poor boys who were called in to be sent out to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Ukraine was a horrible word to mention, because about 65,000 of the nicest Jewish boys from Hungary, from age 22 to 35 and 40, were called up and sent away over there to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They got this invitation, it was-- SOS it was called, like it was an important call.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were not on army duty, but they were just forced labor, helping [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for the Hungarian and the German armies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was the official name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the truth is that the Hungarian Nazi government, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whether they did it on their own or not-- I know after the war I read about-- a book about-- from one of the defense ministers of Hungary, this is most criminal thing, because most of people, most of soldier-- any soldier who is out on the-- in the fire line more than a few months, he is sent home and exchanged.",
      "word_count": 75
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "These boys were sent there not to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the purpose.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And about 50,000 or 60,000 were perished over there in the horrible cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were not dressed for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They did not have food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were surrounded with Ukrainian, Hungarian butchers, who were looking for every occasion to-- I had two uncles who were-- somebody was telling me, he says, they just froze.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They had hospitals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were-- and there was over there a-- they call it mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were supposed to pick mines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "These mines were connected to each other every few-- maybe 100 meter, 100 yard away, they were connected with-- with wires.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
